- create a Set and move the values in. a Set will only keep unique values, so no duplicates would ever be included. We can then convert this back to an array if needed.

- Iterate through the array checking values using Array.includes().


const nums = [1, 1, 2, 2, 3, 3, 3];

// Creating a Set process
